data.description: Available for a short-term lease only! This is a cute two-story townhouse located in a quiet cul-de-sac. Only minutes from Texas A&M, Blinn, and Bryan's new up-and-coming Midtown Park makes the location ideal! The kitchen was recently renovated and brand-new stainless steel appliances were added. The primary bedroom and bathroom are located downstairs and two bedrooms upstairs share a bathroom. Large mature trees provide amazing shade in the large backyard. Owner is paying all utilities and all appliances are included. Schedule your showing today!
